Burning bootloader:
    connect stk500 and chip each on their own power supply. Leave the VCC pin disconnected from the ISP header
    
    avrdude  -c stk500 -pm1284p -P /dev/ttyUSB9 -b115200 -B1 -U lfuse:w:0xF7:m -U hfuse:w:0xDE:m
    avrdude  -c stk500 -pm1284p -P /dev/ttyUSB9 -b115200 -B1 -U flash:w:optiboot_atmega1284p.hex:i

The, using FTDI:
avrdude -vvv -pm1284p -P /dev/ttyUSB10 -carduino -b115200 -U flash:w:firmware.hex:i
